      "review_summary": "The PR adds a skip flag, per-account allowlist coverage checks, and regression tests in the shared doctor empty-allowlist scanner.\n\nPR surface: Source +57, Tests +107. Total +164 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main checks the top-level channel record before account records, and PR head still invokes `extraWarningsForAccount` for that parent context; source inspection gives a high-confidence reproduction path.",
      "review_followup": "- [P2] The remaining blocker is a narrow scanner/hook repair on this PR branch, and no product decision is required.",
